                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18390513-1570-offence-1 t18390513-cd-88"></join>20th of April</rs>, 2 pairs of stays, value 3<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18390513-name-606" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18390513-name-606" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
